# Trivy vulnerability suppressions
# Format: CVE-ID [expiry-date] [# reason]
#
# Rules:
# - Every suppression MUST have a comment explaining the reason.
# - Include an expiry date where possible (format: YYYY-MM-DD).
# - Review and remove expired suppressions each sprint.
# - Never suppress CRITICAL CVEs without explicit security team sign-off.
#
# Example (uncomment and adjust when needed):
# CVE-2023-XXXXX 2026-12-31 # Not exploitable: only affects feature X which we don't use
